 role in how we collectively respond to outbreaks.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 0aPublic health laws. 0aPublic healthxInternational cooperation. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / International Relations / General.2bisacsh1 aWenham, Clare, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertBristol UP/Policy Press Complete eBook-Package 2021z978311119675640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781529219357423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781529219357/original  a978-3-11-119675-6  Bristol UP/Policy Press Complete eBook-Package 2021b2021  aGBV-deGruyter-alles